    "id": "R29_226",
    "content": "## TDD for Bug Fixes\n### Process:\n1. **Reproduce the bug with a test**\n2. **Confirm the test fails**\n3. **Fix the bug**\n4. **Confirm the test passes**\n5. **Add additional tests for edge cases**",
    "project": "freshie_aws-mad-libs",
    "file": "test-driven-development.md",
    "first_level": "Quality Assurance",
    "second_level": "Testing Strategy"
  },
  {
    "id": "R29_227",
    "content": "## TDD for Refactoring\n### Process:\n1. **Ensure existing tests pass**\n2. **Add tests for new behavior if needed**\n3. **Refactor implementation**\n4. **Ensure all tests still pass**\n5. **Remove obsolete tests if any**",
    "project": "freshie_aws-mad-libs",
    "file": "test-driven-development.md",
    "first_level": "Quality Assurance",
    "second_level": "Testing Strategy"
  },
